 as a prosecutor in the state of new jersey and was later a partner in the accounting firm of coopers  lybrand during the jimmy carter administration oleary was assistant administrator of the federal energy administration general counsel of the community services administration and administrator of the economic regulatory administration at the newlycreated department of energy in  oleary established with her husband the consulting firm of oleary  associates serving as vice president and general counsel from  to  she worked as an executive vice president of the northern states power company also oleary was nominated to be secretary of energy in  by president bill clinton during this time she was often accused of traveling too frequently and spending lavishly on her accommodations she apologized to congressional committees in  for spending which exceeded limits on the funds appropriated for travel and resigned in january  it was later revealed that chinagate scandal figure johnny chung claimed that oleary met with chinese oil officials after chung had donated  to olearys favorite charity africare currently oleary serves as president of fisk university in nashville her honors and affiliations have included board of directors ual corp parent company of united airlines alchemix corp scottish re ltd aes corp and world wildlife fund board of trustees and cochair the campaign for a new century morehouse college phi beta kappa oleary is widowed she has one son carl rollins  an attorney in washington dc reference wikimedia foundation  th avenue north suite st petersburg fl  to become a lawyer person  name  oleary hazel related videos  career advice public policy pt  dr samuel myers jr economist educator and activist dr samuel myers jr shares some factual advice to those interested a career in public policy average select ratingcancel ratingpoorokaygoodgreatawesome your rating none average   votes average select ratingcancel ratingpoorokaygoodgreatawesome your rating none aver